 Toj ventan n-chi b´et oxe b´alun, kab´e kyxol qe jlu n-chi ky-q´i´n toxin, a t-xilen
najnab´il. E kub´ tz´aq tuk´e jun t-xu´k t-xe t-xaq Harry, extzen aju´ b´alun tmij, aju´ nimxix
ex gris, keeled right over ex kubʼ ten mintiʼ in bʼet. Attaq jun matij pakb’al k’alo’n kyi’j tqan.
