kukxtoq in bʼaj t-xoʼn tibʼ tukʼil yolbʼil otoq tzʼok tbʼiʼn.
 ¿Tiqu´n myia jun xjal tzaj tq´ama´n te? Dumbledore, Hagrid, Mr. Weasley, Cornelius Fudge... tiqu´n
mintiʼ jun xjal otoq tzaj tqʼamaʼn qa otoq che kyim tman Harry tuʼnju otoq che kyim tbʼanel kyamiw
xi tq´o´n kye?
